methods.tryGetNextSlice:
Tries to get the next slice from one of the inner QueueReaders. Uses data in the 'controlReader' to figure out
 which QueueReader the next slice is coming from.

:param bs: (io.deephaven.csv.containers.ByteSlice) - If the method returns true, the contents of this parameter will be updated.
:return: (boolean) true if there is more data, and the ByteSlice has been populated. Otherwise, false.

text: Companion to the DenseStorageWriter. See the documentation there for details.
